ReportBundle.ReportXML: <Report ReportGID="211e1351-01c4-4177-be27-9bb904b2819a" ReportUseType="2" ReportType="5" ReportName="Dry Matter Intake by Pen Type" Description="Dry Matter Intake grouped by Pen Type with the ability to show Pens and Dates" CreatedDT="2013-07-17T09:11:05.493" ModifiedDT="2014-05-19T16:02:20.677" ModifiedBy="VAS" ConcurrencyTS="AAAAAAAAKbE=" ReportVersion="0" />

ReportQuery.ReportQueryText: <QueryBundle> <QueryText>select PrimaryPenType, PenName, ReportDate, DMQty, AvgPenCount, Cost from ( select PrimaryPenType, coalesce(pcc2.AvgPenCount, pcc.AvgPenCount) as AvgPenCount, l.LocationName as PenName, convert(date, it.TransactionDT) as ReportDate, it.DMPct * dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.UnitQuantity, c.MediumMeasurementType) as DMQty, dbo.GetFifoCost(it.UnitQuantity, it.InventoryItemGID, fsmi.SourceLocationGID, it.TransactionDT) as Cost, DropRowNum = row_number() over (partition by it.InventoryTransactionGID order by it.UnitQuantity, it2.UnitQuantity) from InventoryTransaction it join Pen p on p.LocationGID = it.ToLocationGID join Location l on l.LocationGID = p.LocationGID cross apply (select top 1 PenTypeName as PrimaryPenType from PenPenType ppt join PenType pt on pt.PenTypeGID = ppt.PenTypeGID where ppt.PenGID = p.PenGID order by ppt.IsPrimary desc) ppt cross apply (select top 1 [Count] as AvgPenCount from PenCountChange pcc where pcc.PenGID = p.PenGID and pcc.CreatedDT <= it.TransactionDT and InventoryItemType = 3 order by pcc.CreatedDT desc) pcc cross apply (select avg([Count]) as AvgPenCount from PenCountChange pcc where pcc.PenGID = p.PenGID and convert(date, pcc.CreatedDT) = convert(date, it.TransactionDT) and InventoryItemType = 3) pcc2 join Company c on c.CompanyGID = l.CompanyGID join FeedingScheduleDrop fsd on fsd.FeedingScheduleDropGID = it.TransactionSourceGID join FeedingScheduleLoad fl on fl.FeedingScheduleLoadGID = fsd.FeedingScheduleLoadGID join FeedingScheduleMixInstruction fsmi on fsmi.InventoryItemGID = it.InventoryItemGID and fsmi.FeedingScheduleMixGID = fl.FeedingScheduleMixGID join InventoryTransaction it2 on it2.TransactionSourceGID = fsmi.FeedingScheduleMixInstructionGID ) z where DropRowNum = 1</QueryText> <PreQueryText /> </QueryBundle>
